    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into luxury with a vehicle that is in absolute mint condition! This car looks and feels exactly like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor, featuring a flawless exterior and a pristine interior. It's a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants a like-new driving experience at a great value!",
